          <h2> Autonomous Under-Vehicle Inspection Robot with PRRR Manipulator </h2>
          <p> Vehicle undercarriage inspection is typically performed using bulky equipment and manual operation, 
              making the process slow, labor-intensive, and difficult to deploy in confined spaces. But how about
              a compact robotic inspection system capable of navigating and positioning sensors or tools for 
              detailed inspection tasks? </p>

          </p>
